1934;;Music in the Air;;American;;Joe May;;Gloria Swanson, John Boles;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Music_in_the_Air_(film);;Opera star Frieda Hotzfelt (Gloria Swanson) spars with librettist Bruno Mahler (John Boles). Aspiring songwriter Karl Roder (Douglass Montgomery) stumbles into their stormy relationship.